## 🤖 Phase 8: Auto Design System (From ui-ux-pro-max)

### 8.1. Generate Design System via Script
Using data from `.shared/ui-ux-pro-max/` (50+ styles, 97 palettes, 57 fonts):

```bash
# Generate full design system (RECOMMENDED)
python3 .agent/.shared/ui-ux-pro-max/scripts/search.py "<product_type> <industry> <keywords>" --design-system -p "Project Name"

# Save design system to project
python3 .agent/.shared/ui-ux-pro-max/scripts/search.py "<query>" --design-system --persist -p "Project Name"
```

### 8.2. Search by Domain
```bash
python3 .agent/.shared/ui-ux-pro-max/scripts/search.py "<keyword>" --domain <domain>
```

| Domain | Use when | Example |
|--------|----------|---------|
| `style` | Finding UI style | `--domain style "glassmorphism dark"` |
| `chart` | Finding chart type | `--domain chart "real-time dashboard"` |
| `ux` | Best practices | `--domain ux "animation accessibility"` |
| `typography` | Finding fonts | `--domain typography "elegant luxury"` |
| `landing` | Landing structure | `--domain landing "hero social-proof"` |

### 8.3. Stack Guidelines
```bash
python3 .agent/.shared/ui-ux-pro-max/scripts/search.py "<keyword>" --stack html-tailwind
```
Stacks: `html-tailwind`, `react`, `nextjs`, `vue`, `svelte`, `swiftui`, `react-native`, `flutter`, `shadcn`

---

## 📋 Phase 9: Professional UI Checklist

### Icons & Visual
- [ ] Don't use emoji as UI icons (use SVG: Heroicons, Lucide)
- [ ] Icons consistent in size (w-6 h-6)
- [ ] Brand logos accurate (from Simple Icons)

### Interaction
- [ ] All clickable elements have `cursor-pointer`
- [ ] Hover states have visual feedback
- [ ] Smooth transitions (150-300ms)
- [ ] Focus states for keyboard navigation

### Light/Dark Mode
- [ ] Light mode text contrast sufficient (4.5:1 minimum)
- [ ] Glass/transparent elements visible in light mode
- [ ] Borders visible in both modes

### Layout
- [ ] Floating navbar has spacing from edges
- [ ] No content hidden behind fixed navbar
- [ ] Responsive: 375px, 768px, 1024px, 1440px
- [ ] No horizontal scroll on mobile

### Accessibility
- [ ] Images have alt text
- [ ] Form inputs have labels
- [ ] `prefers-reduced-motion` respected

